{"tid":2101850,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解從來冇人講泛民冇論述","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T09:08:42.000Z","uid":126889,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68883a11ae67963c9d51ea49cd572bfb2a0d1194","tid":2101850,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"泛民從來只有一個論述<br />\n就係司徒老賊班人未收皮前既<br />\n民主中國+民主回歸論<br />\n依家老泛民都冇得7788<br />\n上面個套都冇人當回事<br />\n其實泛民已經論述真空左幾年<br />\n但係就反個頭話人冇論述<br />\n<br />\n事實就係岩岩相反<br />\n本土派就係最有論述<br />\n連咁多人憎既陳雲熱狗都幾本城邦論<br />\n之後又會有人話論述唔入屋佢錯<br />\n光復香港時代革命叫到成香港都知仲未認係要獨立<br />\nSpin黎spin去咩時代抗疫又各自解讀<br />\n一陣大家又話要時間表<br />\n<br />\n其實大家唔係要論述<br />\n個個要既係既成事實<br />\n久唔久就有人開po又話冇論述<br />\n一班人解釋完下班又問咩論述<br />\n班人係要一比火燒親<br />\n就突然識講啲論述<br />\n我勸本土志士真係少浪費時間 發展自己勢力算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141d2c7dc54377078dff14165913230f365c32b3","tid":2101850,"uid":50275,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"泛民論述：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「民主最黑暗一天」論<br />\n<br />\n「贏五比一」論<br />\n<br />\n「中國有民主，香港先有民主」論<br />\n<br />\n「over my dead body」論"},{"pid":"30a80ae4a9e5d34c3f057d2cdbb19fe505971533","tid":2101850,"uid":38182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"有理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab132ba4e86d2281e0933c618d73dc575b7325fe","tid":2101850,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"141d2c7dc54377078dff14165913230f365c32b3","tid":2101850,"uid":50275,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"泛民論述：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「民主最黑暗一天」論<br />\n<br />\n「贏五比一」論<br />\n<br />\n「中國有民主，香港先有民主」論<br />\n<br />\n「over my dead body」論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"明明最撚含糊就係班人 <br />\n個名掛住民主 但實現民主既論述就係上面果啲<br />\n仲問係咪本土就要投<br />\n<br />\n咁就緊係啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4080357240866ca43bc40375dc3424d0206b48cd","tid":2101850,"uid":242393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6ERcam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6ERcam.jpg&h=784ed40f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"533717696e8f08823c28f6ae3ea148de82c93f0a","tid":2101850,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"over my dead body 論有內涵"},{"pid":"5017d3eaa23e745705847334e0c345e8266acacb","tid":2101850,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"533717696e8f08823c28f6ae3ea148de82c93f0a","tid":2101850,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"over my dead body 論有內涵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"靚仔 好條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cf1c508bac01774a5d9832732460eb17f94327","tid":2101850,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"「其實大家唔係要論述」<br />\n所以泛民無論述有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓豬邏輯有啲混亂啵<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民無論述係真<br />\n但聽七初選討壇，發現民主黨其實都有既，就係35+後民生議案會投贊成<br />\n本土派就係所有議案都會反對<br />\n<br />\n路線分歧無對錯，大家想行邊條路就由我地選民去揀"},{"pid":"ae2984f665a6a525a413b96894caf4441ea385dd","tid":2101850,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"[quote]「其實大家唔係要論述」<br />\n所以泛民無論述有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓豬邏輯有啲混亂啵<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民無論述係真<br />\n但聽完初選論壇，發現民主黨其實都有既，就係35+後民生議案會投贊成<br />\n本土派就係所有議案都會反對<br />\n<br />\n路線分歧無對錯，大家想行邊條路就由我地選民去揀"},{"pid":"561780f433c79ca7c63f75